{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DDeaJkKU6cTRJquiskihSG","type":"tool_result","content":"  3730→\n  3731→| # | Action | Priority | Owner |\n  3732→|---|--------|----------|-------|\n  3733→| 1 | **Kill the ralph process** | CRITICAL | Human |\n  3734→| 2 | Fix ralph to re-read sprint-state.json from disk before every write | HIGH | Dev |\n  3735→| 3 | Add a state guard that rejects status downgrades (done -> review) | HIGH | Dev |\n  3736→| 4 | Add ralph auto-stop when sprint done count = total stories | MEDIUM | Dev |\n  3737→| 5 | Add pre-session state integrity check (compare JSON vs git log) | MEDIUM | Dev |\n  3738→\n  3739→## 8. Sprint Final Status\n  3740→\n  3741→| Metric | Value |\n  3742→|--------|-------|\n  3743→| Stories done | 74/74 (100%) |\n  3744→| Epics done | 17/17 (100%) |\n  3745→| Sprint status | **COMPLETE** |\n  3746→| Remaining work | None |\n  3747→| Blocker | Ralph process with stale state continues to corrupt sprint-state.json |\n  3748→| State corruption fixes | 19 and counting |\n  3749→| Consecutive no-op sessions | 5 |\n  3750→\n  3751→**This is the 5th consecutive no-op session and the 19th state corruption fix. The sprint has been done since session 30. Kill Ralph and stop opening sessions.**\n  3752→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01QH1LFcNWcf1jgonuXHUtsc","session_id":"80517049-b3f7-45f1-a98f-128699cd3a52","uuid":"8d8e5d60-1891-41de-95bf-7fa175919a3b","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:57:22.558Z"}
