{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QH1LFcNWcf1jgonuXHUtsc","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Retrospective for session 36 appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md` and session issues log updated at `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md`.\n\nKey findings:\n- **State corruption fix #20** -- same pattern as always: stories 16-5 through 16-8 reverted from `done` to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`\n- **6th consecutive no-op session** since sprint completion at session 30\n- **Total sprint cost: $684.89** across 5,052 API calls. Verification phase is 54.5% of spend. The \"unknown\" story bucket at $147.80 (21.6%) likely includes orchestrator overhead and no-op session waste.\n- **Root cause unchanged**: ralph's stale in-memory state overwrites sprint-state.json. The `registerStory` guard prevents phantom stories but not status downgrades.\n- **Primary action item**: kill the ralph process and stop opening sessions until the stale-state bug is fixed or a new sprint is planned."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a2f08fc2be8a538f0 (use SendMessage with to: 'a2f08fc2be8a538f0' to continue this agent)\n<usage>total_tokens: 41733\ntool_uses: 11\nduration_ms: 99443</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"80517049-b3f7-45f1-a98f-128699cd3a52","uuid":"daf83457-3f04-48c2-b634-794651206e23","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:58:33.488Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Run a session retrospective for the current sprint session.\n\nSprint status: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/sprint-status.yaml\nSession issues log: _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md\nCost report: Run `codeharness stats --save` to generate the cost report. Read `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/cost-report.md` and include cost analysis in the retrospective.\n\nContext: This was a no-op session (session 36). The sprint-state.json had state corruption — stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 were stuck at `review` status despite having been verified and committed (git log confirms \"verified and done\" commits and proof documents exist). The parent orchestrator fixed the corruption by updating sprint-state.json and sprint-status.yaml to mark all 4 stories as `done` and epic-16 as `done`. Sprint total updated from 70/74 to 74/74.\n\nThis is the same recurring state corruption issue that has been happening across many sessions (see session issues log for prior instances).\n\nProduce a retrospective that covers:\n1. **Session summary** — no-op, state corruption fix only\n2. **Issues analysis** — recurring state corruption is the primary issue\n3. **Cost analysis** — from the cost report\n4. **What went well** — quick identification and fix of corruption\n5. **What went wrong** — state corruption recurred again (session 36!)\n6. **Lessons learned** — the root cause of state corruption needs a permanent fix\n7. **Action items** — categorized by urgency\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md. Since a retro for today already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"a2f08fc2be8a538f0","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Retrospective for session 36 appended to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-27.md` and session issues log updated at `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md`.\n\nKey findings:\n- **State corruption fix #20** -- same pattern as always: stories 16-5 through 16-8 reverted from `done` to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`\n- **6th consecutive no-op session** since sprint completion at session 30\n- **Total sprint cost: $684.89** across 5,052 API calls. Verification phase is 54.5% of spend. The \"unknown\" story bucket at $147.80 (21.6%) likely includes orchestrator overhead and no-op session waste.\n- **Root cause unchanged**: ralph's stale in-memory state overwrites sprint-state.json. The `registerStory` guard prevents phantom stories but not status downgrades.\n- **Primary action item**: kill the ralph process and stop opening sessions until the stale-state bug is fixed or a new sprint is planned."}],"totalDurationMs":99443,"totalTokens":41733,"totalToolUseCount":11,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":718,"cache_read_input_tokens":40719,"output_tokens":295,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":718},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
